{"tid":1638546,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［超合作］知唔知你哋而家返學即係非法集會？","createTime":"2019-10-08T10:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:50:19.000Z","uid":276262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02ed54a0177ff674e0d7cb223c64bd9de17690fd","tid":1638546,"uid":276262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:49:11.000Z","msg":"跟據教育局份有關蒙面法既文件，返學唔比蒙面，而蒙面法規定只係遊行集會唔比蒙面，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇話返學唔比蒙</span><br />\n所以，教育局話返學唔比蒙面，意思就係，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">返學係集會</span><br />\n而學校冇申請，即係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">非法集會！</span><br />\n<br />\n為免誤墮法網，你哋而家應該：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1, 唔好返學</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2, 要求學校每日、每班、每堂，獨立申請不反對通知書</span><br />\n<br />\n記住，保護自己，唔好因為返學而誤墮法網。"},{"pid":"cb9618ebd87fa92bb59bafb3507c9400237071cf","tid":1638546,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:50:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}